- ajout de son sur la video :
    - test fairseq : https://docs.coqui.ai/en/dev/inference.html
    - Enlever les points des phrases ? Splitter les phrases moi-meme ? ===> D'abord tester en ne splittant pas les phrases
    - https://github.com/myshell-ai/MeloTTS pour english, spanish, french, chinese, japanese and korean
        You can use moviepy library to do that. Behind the scenes, it uses ffmpeg to merge audio and video.

        import moviepy.editor as mp

        video_path = 'Path to video file'
        audio_path = 'Path to audio file'
        output_path = 'Path to output video+audio file'

        video = mp.VideoFileClip(video_path)
        audio = mp.AudioFileClip(audio_path)

        video = video.set_audio(audio)

        video.write_videofile(output_path)
    - supported TTS/XTTS-2 : ['en', 'es', 'fr', 'de', 'it', 'pt', 'pl', 'tr', 'ru', 'nl', 'cs', 'ar', 'zh-cn', 'hu', 'ko', 'ja', 'hi']
    - corpus de voix : https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/en/datasets
    - voice cleaning from xtts : https://huggingface.co/spaces/coqui/xtts/blob/main/app.py
    - doc XTTS : https://docs.coqui.ai/en/dev/models/xtts.html
    - WARNING : There's text lenght in all languages, different

